divs: Sighting Detailsi was at work and outside taking our garbage out and i looked up to the west sky and i seen this object spinning around in the sky and it got faster and shot up through the cloud.it was a sunny day and not may clouds that day.i know it was not a plane or bird..it was weird,it was under a cloud,spinning and shot strait up above the cloud and it was gone.
